  4 . Lun7 chhai7 bok8-chu2 , hau3 bok8-chu2 e5 put-thong
  Lun7 put-thong u7 kui2-na7 hang7 e5 ian5- kou3 . Sin5-hun5 boe7 tit-thang lai5 hu7 ti7 sin5- chu2--nih8 . Lang5 tiam3-teh kong2 u7 sin5 tiam3 ti7 sin5-chu2--nih8 , m7-si7 m7-chai-kong2 sin5-hun5 tioh8 khi3 im-kan; i si7 kong2 , lang5 u7 sam-hun5 chhit-phek . Chhit-phek bian2 kong2, kan-ta lun7 sam-hun5 chiu7 ho2 . TaN lang5 kong2 sam-hun5 chiu7-si7 kong2, chit8-tiau5 khi3 im-kan, chit8-tiau5 tiam3 bong7-lai7, chit8-tiau5 hu7 sin5-chu2; taN lang5 thai2- tho2 u7 saN-tiau5 sin5-hun5? Na7 chin-chiaN3 u7 saN-tiau5 sin5-hun5, chiu7 kiam2-chhai2 chit-tiau5 hun5 ai3-beh chiah8 , hit-tiau5 hun5 m7- ai3 chiah8, a2-si7 bo5-beh liam5-piN chiah8 ; a2-si7 chit-tiau5 hun5 ai3 beh khun3 , hit-tiau5 hun5 m7-ai3 khun3 , chiu7 kiam2-m7-tioh8 oan-ke saN-phah mah ? Sou2-i2 se3-siok8 teh kong2 sam-hun5 chiah-e5 tai7-chi3, put-ko3 si7 iN7- toan na7-tiaN7, Ki5-sit8 sin5-hun5 chit8-tiau5 na7-tiaN7, sin5-hun5 ki3-jian5 chit8-tiau5, chiu7 hit-tiau5 khi3 tah-loh8 ? Tiam3 ti7 sin5-chu2 a2 m7-si7 ? M7-si7 ; khi3 im-kan . Lang5 siN- cheng5 kiaN5 ho2 , oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou , sin3 hok-im, tit-tioh8 Kiu3-chu2 e5 siok8-choe7 , ThiN-pe7 e5 sia3-choe7 , Seng3-sin5 e5 teng5-siN , si2-au7 sin- khu kui thou2 , sin5-hun5 chiuN7 thian-tong5 , tit-tioh8 eng2-oan2 e5 hok-khi3 ; siat-su2 choe3 Mou5-kui2 e5 kiaN2, hong3-chhiong3 su-iok8 kiaN5-phaiN2 , chiu7 sin5-hun5 tim5-lun5 te7-gek8 , thai2 oe7 koh siN chit8-tiau5 sin5-hun5 lai5 hu7 ti7 bok8-chu2-ah ? 
  U7 lang5 pok kong2 , Hun5 sui-bong2 chit8- tiau5 na7-tiaN7 , chong2-si7 iu5-goan5 oe7 hu7 ti7 sin5-chu2 ; in-ui7 na7 kiaN5-ho2 , i e5 sin5-hun5 kau3 thian-tong5 iau2-ku2 iah8 oe7 tiam3 ti7 sin5-chu2 ; na7 si7 kiaN5-phaiN2 koaiN ti7 te7-gek8, theng3-hau7 chhiaN2 he5-siuN7 lai5 phah te7-gek8 , phah liau2-au7 i oe7 chhut--lai5 , an2-ni i kiam2-boe7 lai5 hu7 ti7 sin5-chu2 mah ? 
  Goa2 kong2 , M7 si7 an2-ni ; thian-tong5 si7 chiau5-chng5 ho2 , toa7 hok-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7 , se3-kan ong5-kiong a2-si7 te7-it song2 e5 sou2- chai7 kap i iah8 boe7 pi2--tit ; lang5 i2-keng kau3 hit-ui7 , khoaN3 se3-kan te7-it song2 e5 toa7- chhu3 , siong7-chhiaN2 chhin-chhiuN7 pun3-so3 , ho5-hong3 hit-te3 piN2-pang-a2 , i thai2-tho2 beh lai5 tiam3 ? Lun7 kau3 chhiaN2 he5-siuN7 phah te7-gek8 e5 tai7-chi3, si7 koh-khah lam7- sam2 . In-ui7 te7-gek8 si7 bo5 heng5, hit e5 ui7 si7 Siong7-te3 pi7-pan7 teh heng5-hoat8 phaiN2- lang5--e5, ti7-hia thang5 boe7 si2 , he2 boe7 hoa; kiam2-si7 he5-siuN7 sou2 oe7 phoa3--tit mah ? Na7 Siong7-te3 liah8 lang5 koaiN-loh8 te7-gek8 , he5-siuN7 oe7 pang3 i chhut--lai5, an2-ni he5- siuN7 pi2 Siong7-te3 khah-toa7, pai3 he5-siuN7 chiu7 kau3-giah8 . Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 kong2, M7-si7 an2-ni, he5-siuN7 put-ko3 si7 thok put8 ka7 Siong7-te3 kiu5-cheng5 na7-tiaN7 , thai2-tho2 kong2 pi2 Siong7-te3 khah toa7 ? Goa2 kong2 , Iah8 m7-si7 an2-ni ; lang5 hou7 koaN-hu2 liah8- khi3 koaiN-kaN, kiam2-chhai2 khi3 thok ho2 se3- thau5 e5 lang5 khi3 kiu5-cheng5, siong7-chhiaN2 tioh8 khoaN3 i-e5 an3 si7 chaiN2-iuN7, bo5 tek- khak kian3-kiu5 kian3-pang3 ; ho5-hong3 lang5 hou7 Siong7-te3 koaiN, he5-siuN7 thok-put8 , put8 kian3 kiu5 , Siong7-te3 kian3-pang3 . An2-ni lang5 u7 phaiN2, Siong7-te3 bo5 pan7, si7 Siong7- te3 bo5 kong-to7 ; u7 chiN5--e5 chhiaN2 he5-siuN7 phah te7-gek8 , chiu7 oe7 chhut te7-gek8 , bo5 chiN5 thang chhiaN2 he5-siuN7 lai5 phah--e5, chiu7 boe7 chhut te7-gek8 ; an2-ni si7 iu2- chian5-chia2 seng , bu5-chian5-chia2 su2 , khoaN3 Siong7-te3 choe3 tham-koan u-li7, choe7 tang7 kau3 chaiN2-iuN7 ? 
  An2-ni lang5 e5 sin5-hun5 na7 kau3 thian- tong5 iah8 m7-lai5 hu7 ti7 sin5-chu2 , na7 kau3 te7- gek8 chiu7 eng2-eng2 boe7 tit lai5 ; i2-keng boe7 hu7 sin5-chu2, chiah koh lai5 chhong3 sin5-chu2 , che kiam2 m7-si7 put-thong mah ? 
  Koh khah put-thong--e5 , chiu7-si7 u7-e5 si7 chit8-lang5 ia7 u7 kui2-na7 sian sin5-chu2 ; chhin-chhiuN7 Chiang-chiu siok8 u7 chit8 sou2- chai7 siN3 Lim5--e5, kui2-chap8 ni5 cheng5 Tng5- mng5-hoan2 kau3 in chiu7 chhiaN2 sin5-chu2 chau2, u7-e5 chhiaN2 kong e5 sin5-chu2, u7-e5 chhiaN2 ma2 e5 sin5-chu2 ; tui3 si3-soaN3 liau2-au7 bo5 koh choe3 tui , in-ui7 chhiaN2 kong e5 sin5-chu2--e5 kah chhiaN2 ma2 e5 sin5-chu2--e5 tioh8 chhiaN2 ma2 e5 sin5-chu2 lai5 chiu7 in; chhiaN2 ma2--e5 kong2 , Goan2 kah hiah kian3-siau3 cha-bou2 chhe7 lin2 ta-pou ! Tui3 an2-ni , chhiaN2 kong e5 sin5-chu2--e5 tioh8 chhong3 chit8-sin ma2 e5 sin5-chu2, chhiaN2 ma2--e5 , koh chhong3 chit8-sin kong e5 sin5-chu2 . Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, hap8-li2 mah ? Chit8-lang5 kiam2 u7 nng7 e5 sin5 thang hu7 nng7-sin bok8-chu2 ah ? Sit8-chai7 toa7 put- thong . 
  2 . Siat-su2 oe7 lai5 hu7 , i iah8 m7-lai5 . Lang5 sou2 ai3 chhin-kun7--e5 , tek-khak tioh8 i-e5 tang5-lui7 , bo5 tang5-lui7 chiu7 m7 saN-oa2 . Sou2- i2 cha2 eng7 lang5 lai5 choe3 si , tioh8 eng7 ka- ki7 e5 kiaN2-sun chiah oe7 choe3--tit ; si7 in- ui7 kong2 , goa7-siN3 e5 kiaN2-sun m7-si7 ka-ki7 e5 kut-jiok8 hiat-meh8 sou2 chhut--e5, sin5 m7 lai5 oa2 . Chong2-si7 iau2-ku2 si7 lang5, bok8- chu2 si7 chha5 , si2-si2 e5 mih8 , sin5 kam2 beh oa2 ? Siat-su2 beh lai5 oa2 , chhi3-mng7 chit8-te3-a2 e5 pang u7 kau3-giah8 thang hou7 sin5 khia7-khi2 a2-bo5 ? Sou2 kong2 sou2-choe3 long2 si7 bo5 cheng5-li2 bo5 i3-su3 ; lin2 chhai7 bok8-chu2 e5 lang5 , kan2 m7 ka-ki7 seng2-chhat khoaN3 teh ? 
  3 . Lang5 teh chhai7 bok8-chu2 , i3-su3 si7 kong2 na7 bo5 hau3--i , chiu7 oe7 choe3 iau-kui2 . Na7 chin-chiaN3 u7-iaN2, chiu7 tioh8 soa3 choe3 hou7 i chheng7 , in-ui7 bo5 chiah8 oe7 iau , chiu7 bo5 chheng7 oe7 koaN5 . Cheng-siN bo5 chheng7 si7 in-ui7 i u7 mng5, kiam2 lang5 si2-liau2 sin5- hun5 oe7 hoat-mng5 ? Na7 an2-ni si7 khoan2- thai7 chou2-kong choe3 cheng-siN , koh-khah put-hau3 . TaN lin2 chhai7 bok8-chu2--e5 , bat eng7 mih8 hau3 sin5-chu2 , kam2 bat soa3 choe3 saN-a2-khou3 hou7 i chheng7 ; na7-kah boe7 koaN5 chu7-jian5 iah8 boe7 iau , ki3-jian5 boe7 iau chu7- jian5 bian2-che3 , ki3-jian5 bian2-che3 chiu7 soa3 bian2 chhai7 bok8-chu2 si7 beng5 . 
  5 . Lun7 bo5 chhai7 bok8-chu2 , bo5 che3 bok8-chu2 si7 long2 bo5 thang hiam5 . 
  Lang5 hiam5 goan2 jip8-kau3 e5 lang5 bo5 chhai7 bok8-chu2 si7 bo5-chou2 bo5-kong, su7- put-ti goan2 bo5 chhai7 bo5 che3 si7 u7 tioh8 e5 ian5-kou3 , hit-e5 ian5-kou3 u7 nng7-hang7 . 
  1 . Chou2-kong boe7 lai5 chiah8 . 
  Chha5-kho2 cha2 seng3-ong5 seng3-jin5 siat chit-e5 che3 e5 hoat-tou7 , pun2 m7-si7 ui7 chou2- kong , sit8-chai7 si7 ui7-tioh8 kiaN2-sun ; hau3- keng kong2 , “ Khi3 chong-biau7--nih8 ti3- keng3 , si7 beh bo5 boe7-ki3-tit pe7-bu2 ” . Tan5- kiong kong2, “ Khi2-thau5 si2 , eng7 bah-hu2 sng-chhou3 lai5 koan3-tian7 , tit-beh khi3 tai5 e5 si5 , eng7 ngou2-seng lai5 che3 , tai5-liau2 to3-- lai5 , koh-chai3 hau3 , ( che si7 jit8 tiong-tau3 ti7 i si2 e5 pang5-lai7 hau3, ) be7 bat khoaN3-kiN3 i lai5 chiah8 , tui3 teng2-tai7 i2-lai5 , long2 bo5 pang3-soah , si7 ai3 lang5 bo5 poe7 i e5 chhin . ” Hong-ki3 kong2, “ Siu-cheng2 chong-biau7 , keng3 che3-su7 , si7 beh ka3 peh-siN3 tui-siuN7 iu2-hau3 . ” Che beng5-beng5 si7 kong2 , che3 m7-si7 in-ui7 chou2-kong oe7 lai5 chiah8 , put- ko3 si7 hou7 lang5 oe7 siau3-liam7 i e5 chou2-kong na7-tiaN7 . Lun7 si2--e5 boe7 lai5 kam3-lap8 oah8- lang5 e5 che3-su7, beng5-li2--e5, ka-ki7 oe7 chai. Au-iong5 Siu Long5-kong-chhian pian2- ki3--nih8 kong2, “ Che3 chin7-choe7 mih8 , m7- tat8-tioh8 eng7 chio2-chio2 mih8 hou7 pe7-bu2 oah8-oah8 e5 si5 thang chiah8 . ” Cheng-chu2 kong2 , “ Choe3 kiaN2 e5 lang5 beh hong7-iong7 , pe7-bu2 to boe7 theng3-hau7--tit , ( i3-su3 si7 si2 , ) sou2-i2 thai5-gu5 lai5 che3 , m7 tat8-tioh8 than3 pe7-bu2 te7-teh eng7 koe ti lai5 hou7 i chiah8 khah- ho2 . ” Chiah-e5 beng5-beng5 si7 kong2, che3- su7 m7-si7 beh-hou7 chou2-kong lai5 chiah8, put- ko3 si7 beh hou7 lang5 bo5 boe7-ki3-tit i e5 pe7-bu2 na7-tiaN7 . Chai7 sian-ong5 lip8-che3 e5 pun2- i3 si7 kong2-kio3 pe7-bu2 si7 pun2-goan5, pe7-bu2 si2 chiu7 pun2-goan5 choat8; pun2-goan5 kah choat8 , chiu7 iu2-hau3 e5 sim iah8 choat8 ; m7- ku2 pe7-bu2 si7 chit8-si3-lang5 sou2 tioh8 siau3- liam7--e5, sou2-i2 choe3 che3 e5 hoat-tou7, hou7 lang5 ti7 choat8-hau3 e5 tiong-kan boe7 liam5-piN choat8, si7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 eng7 chit-e5 che3 choe3 cheng2, chai ti7 lang5 e5 sim, hou7 lang5 oe7 siN-chhut iu2-hau3; lip8-che3 e5 pun2-i3 put-ko3 si7 an2-ni. Kho2-sioh au7-tai7 e5 thak8-chheh lang5 , bo5 beng5-pek8 sian-ong5 lip8-che3 e5 i3-su3, lam7-sam2 kong2 kau3 hiah- e5 im-iong5, li2-khi3 , chou2-kong lai5 kam3-lap8 e5 tai7-chi3 , soa3 siat peh-siN3 lang5 che3 sam- tai7 kap si2-chou2 e5 su7 , choe3 au7-tai7 im5-su7 e5 kia7-a2, hoan7-le2 , ke3-hun7, siong hong-siok8 , pai7 jin5-lun5 , iau2-ku2 teh phah-sng3 i si7 seng3-kau3 iu2-kong e5 jin5-sin5 , long2 m7-chai si7 sian-ong5 e5 choe7-jin5 . Koh khah thang oan3-hun7--e5, chiu7-si7 Sek-kau3, To7-kau3 , liu5- heng5 thong-kok, hai7-lang5 phian3-lang5, i sou2 kong2 e5 iu2-hau3 long2 put-chai7 siN- cheng5 e5 hong7-iong7, iau3-kin2 si7 chai7-ti7 si2- au7 e5 che3 , pai3 , choe3-chio3, siu-chai , chhiau- tou7, pai3-put8 , liam7-keng, phah te7-gek8 ; lun7-kau3 khiok-le2, siau3-gi5 , loe7-chek, te7- chu2-chit , hau3-keng3, i2-kip8 hoan7-na7 lun7- khi2 lang5 hok8-sai7 pe7-bu2 e5 tai7-chi3--e5 , it- khai3 bo5 kong2-khi2 ; sou2-i2 i-e5 oe7 hou7 lang5 koe7 hoaN-hi2, in-ui7 bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 kou2-le2 e5 khu-sok ; tui3 an2-ni lang5-lang5 siu7 i be5- hek8, poe7 sian-ong5 ka3 lang5 iu2-hau3 e5 ho2- sim, chi2-u7 siu2 Sek-kau3 To7-kau3 e5 iN7-toan sia5-soat, i2-kip8 sian-ong5 lip8-che3 e5 le2-lou7, gong7-gong7 phah-sng3 na7 oe7 an2-ni , chiu7 thang sng3 choe3 iu2-hau3 , hai3-ah ! ChaiN2- iuN7 khoaN3 iu2-hau3 kau3-chiah sio2-khoa2, kau3-chiah khoai3 ? Lun7-kau3 goan2 seng3- kau3 tiong e5 lang5 chin-chiaN3 u7 hap8 sian- ong5 ka3 lang5 iu2-hau3 e5 ho2-sim, put-ko3 bo5 siu2 i lip8-che3 e5 le2-lou7, lang5 chiu7 kio3 goan2 choe3 than3-hoan , bo5-kong bo5-chou2 , kam2 m7-si7 oan-ong2 mah ? Lun7 che3, put-ko3 si7 ka3-lang5 iu2-hau3 e5 hoat-tou7 na7-tiaN7 , na7 oe7 iu2-hau3 chiu7 kau3-giah8, lang5 na7 oe7 than3 goan2 e5 to7-li2, jip8 goan2 e5 kau3, sin3 goan2 e5 seng3-keng , chu7-jian5 siong5-siong5 oe7 iu2- hau3 . mih-sai2 tek-khak tioh8 che3 ah ? Phi3- lun7 tang-thiN chheng7 hiu5 , he7-thiN chheng7 koah , che si7 cha2 e5 khoan2; taN na7 m7 chheng7 hiu5 beh chheng7 ni5-saN, m7 chheng7 koah beh chheng7 kang-sai , thai2-tho2 boe7- choe3-tit ? Tang-thiN chheng7 hiu5, he7 thiN chheng7 koah, put-ko3 si7 beh lang5 khoai3- oah8 na7-tiaN7, na7 khoai3-oah8 , chiu7 tang- thiN chheng7 ni5-saN, joah8-thiN chheng7 kang-sai , chu7-jian5 oe7 choe3-tit . Chun5 tioh8 u7 eng7 phang5, che si7 chun5 e5 khoan2 ; taN m7 eng7 phang5 , si7 beh eng7 chhia , kiam2 oe7 tit-thang kong2 , che m7-si7 chun5, thai2-tho2 u7 chun5 bo5 chun5-phang5 ? Phang5 put-ko3 si7 choe3 hou7 chun5 kiaN5 e5 lou7-eng7 na7-tiaN7, oe7 kiaN5 chiu7 kau3-giah8 , mih-sai2 tek-khak tioh8 phang5 ah ? Sou2-i2 goa2 kong2 oe7 iu2-hau3 khah iau3-kin2, na7 chin-chiaN3 oe7 iu2-hau3 , chiu7 bo5-che3 iah8-bo5 siong-kan . 
  2 . Che3 tsou2-kong hoan2-tng2 si7 tek-tsoe7 Siong7-te3 
  SaN chheng goa7 ni5 cheng5 Siong7-te3 pun2- sin ti7 Se-nai2-soaN thoan5 tsap8 kai3 , hit e5 te7 ji7 kai3 kong2, “ Boh8-tit tiau-khek ngou2-siong7 , thiN-teng2 toe7-e7, tsui2-tiong pah-hang7 mih8, boh8-tit tsng-siong7 chhin-chhiuN7 i, boh8-tit pai3 kui7 , boh8-tit hok8-sai7 ; in-ui7 goa2 Ia5-ho5- hoa lin2-e5 Siong7-te3 , toan3-toan3 boe7 iong5-- tit eng7 pat8-e5 Siong7-te3 kap goa2 pi2 ; oan3- hun7 goa2 e5 lang5 , kang3 tsai-e7 hou7--i , tui3 pe7 kau3 kiaN2 kau3 saN si3 tai7 , thiaN3 goa2 , siu2 goa2 kai3-lut8 e5 lang5 chiu7 kang3 hok-khi3 hou7--i , kau3 chheng pah-tai7 ” . An2-ni , che3 , pai3 , tioh8 Siong7-te3 chiah oe7 kham-tit siu7, lang5 che3 pat8-mih8 , pai3 pat8-mih8 , chiu7 pai3 e5 lang5 , che3 e5 lang5 , i2-kip8 siu7 che3 , siu7 pai3 e5 lang5 , Siong7-te3 long2 beh heng5-hoat8--i . I2-sek-liat8 peh-siN3 hian3-che3 Siong7-te3 , iah8 hian3-che3 pat8-mih8 , Siong7-te3 toa7 siu7-khi3 , kang3 chai-e7 ti7 in-e5 kok . Hi-lut8 ong5 hou7 i-e5 peh-siN3 chheng i choe3 Siong7-te3 , Hi- lut8 hoaN-hi2 , Siong7-te3 hou7 thang5 ka7-si2--i . ( Heng7-toan7 12 : 22 , 23 . ) Ko-ni5-liu5 beh pai3 Pi2-tek , Pi2-tek kin2-kin2 hu5 i kong2 , “ Khi2--lai5 , goa2 iah8-si7 lang5 . ” Lou7-su7-tek e5 lang5 beh che3 Po2-lo5 , Po2-lo5 chhut-lat8 chou2- tong3 , m7-kaN2 siu7 in che3 . ( Heng7-toan7 14 : 13-18 . ) Su3-tou5 Iok-han7 beh pai3 chi2-si7 i e5 thiN-sai3 , thiN-sai3 chou2-chi2--i kong2 , “ M7-thang , li2 chheng-chheng tioh8 pai3 Siong7- te3 . ” ( Bek8-si7-liok8 22 : 8 , 9 . ) Mou5-kui2 kah Ia5-sou pai3--i , Ia5-sou in2 seng3-keng e5 oe7 kong2 , “ Tioh8 pai3 Chu2 li2 e5 Siong7-te3 , tok8- tok8 hok8-sai7--i . ” ( Sin-beng7-ki3 6 : 13 , Ma2- thai3 4 : 10 . ) An2-ni toa7 e5 su3-tou5, seng3 e5 thiN-sai3 , am3-se3 e5 jin5-kun, siong7-chhiaN2 m7-thang pai3 , ho5-hong3 si2-liau2 e5 lang5 . In- ui7 Siong7-te3 si7 chi3-chun bu5 tui3 , tok8-it bu5 ji7 , ban7-lang5 oa2-kho3 i lai5 oah8 , lai5 tin2-tang7 , lai5 ti7-teh , hong5-te3 e5 siN3-mia7 si7 kho3 i chiah oah8 , pe7-bu2 e5 siN3-mia7 iah8 kho3 i chiah oah8 ; pe7-bu2 sui-jian5 pi2 kiaN2 khah toa7 , chong2-si7 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 piN5-piN5 si7 i-e5 lou5-pok8 , hoan7-choe7 e5 lang5 , thai2-tho2 thang liah8 i choe3 chhin-chhiuN7 Siong7-te3 ? Chha5-kho2 chit-e5 che3 e5 tai7- chi3 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 siat , u7 siok8-choe7 e5 che3 , u7 sia7-un e5 che3 , u7 sio-che3, tu5 siok8-choe7 che3 i2-goa7 , ki5-u5--e5 long2 si7 keng3-pai3 sia7- un e5 i3-su3 . Chong2-si7 chiah-e5 che3 , long2-si7 koan-chio3 Kiu3-chu2 , Kiu3-chu2 iau2-be7 kau3 , lang5 tioh8 siu2 chit-e5 le2-sou3 , Kiu3-chu2 i2- keng kau3 , hian3 ka-ki7 choe3 che3 , lai5 siok8 lang5 e5 choe7 , chit8-pai2 chiu7 kau3-giah8 , sou2- i2 chit-e5 le2-sou3 thang hoe3 ; lang5 pai3 Siong7- te3 , na7 sai2 eng7 sim-sin5 , eng7 seng5-sit8, chiah-e5 le2-sou3 long2 m7-sai2 koh kiaN5 . 
