  Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 kong2 , Che3 si7 seng3- jin5 sou2 siat , na7 an2-ni chiu7 seng3-jin5 iah8 u7 ke3-sit mah ? Goa2 in3 kong2 , Thai2-tho2 bo5 ke3-sit ? Lun7 i peng5-seng sou2-kiaN5 tai7- khai3 lai5 kong2 , si7 thang o-lo2 , iau2-ku2 m7- si7 kong2 i long2 bo5 chit8-tiam2-a2 e5 chho3-gou7 . Tong5-tiau5 Li2 Thai3-pek8 kong2 , “ Lang5 to m7-si7 Giau5 Sun3 , thai3-oe7 it-chin7 ho2 ? ” An2- ni i chha-put-to si7 kong2 , chi2-u7 Giau5 Sun3 it-chin7 ho2 na7-tiaN7 , ki5-u5 long2 bo5 . Chong2-si7 lun7 kau3 Giau5 Sun3 , Khong2-chu2 chiu7 kong2 , “ Giau5-Sun3 siong7-ku2 u7 pe7-peng7 .” Lun7 kau3 Khong2-chu2 pun2-sin i ka-ki7 u7 kong2 , “ Na7 oe7 hou7 goa2 ke chiah8 kui2-ni5 , kau3 gou7-chap8 he3 lai5 thak8 iah8-keng , chiu7 bian2 u7 toa7 ke3-sit . ” An2-ni chiu7 iau2-be7 thak8 iah8-keng e5 si5 u7 toa7 ke3-sit, chiu7 thak8 iah8-keng liau2-au7 , iah8 boe7 bian2-tit u7 sio2-khoa2 e5 ke3-sit . Giau5 Sun3 Khong2- chu2 , siong7-chhiaN2 bo5 chiau5-chng5 ho2 , ki5- u5--e5 kiam2-oe7 khah-iaN5 in mah ? Goan2 e5 seng3-keng u7 kong2 , “ Siong7-te3 ti7 thiN-- nih8 , kam3-chhat cheng3-lang5, ai3 chai ki5- tiong u7 hit-ho7 chiau5-chng5 ti3-hui7 , oe7 keng3 Siong7-te3 e5 lang5 a2-bo5 , chiu7 long2-si7 chiu7 sia5 , khi3 cheng3 , be7 u7 kiaN5 ho2 e5 lang5 . ” ( Si-phian 53 : 2 , 3 . ) Ia5-sou kong2 , “ Bo5 chit8-lang5 ho2 , chi2-u7 Siong7-te3 na7-tiaN7 . ” ( Ma2-thai3 19 : 17 . ) Sou2-i2 m7-thang phah- sng3 che3 si7 seng3-jin5 sou2 siat , chiu7 tek- khak si7 bo5 chho3 . Pin5-sim lai5 lun7 , hian7-si5 che3 chou2-sian e5 le2 na7 u7 hap8-li2 , chiu7 put-lun7 u7 chiau3 kou2-hoat a2 bo5 chiau3 kou2-hoat , long2 bo5 iau3-kin2; na7 bo5 hap8-li2 , chiu7 put-lun7 si7 seng3-jin5 sou2 siat , a2 m7-si7 seng3-jin5 sou2 siat , long2 tioh8 pang3-soah . 
